  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate whether and what extent blood pressure
      variability is associated with arterial stiffness and carotid atherosclerosis, furthermore to
      compare the difference in the relationship of the types of blood pressure variability with
      arterial stiffness and carotid atherosclerosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
